# vim: ft=cfg:
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User mukimov@gmail.com
Pass
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel sync-googlemail-default
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel sync-googlemail-github
Far :gmail-remote:Github
Near :gmail-local:github
Create Near

Group googlemail
Channel sync-googlemail-default
Channel sync-googlemail-github

